## Agent Lookup (IMPORTANT)

When delegating tasks, look up agents by their **agent name** (not role) in agents.yml.
Agent names may differ from roles (e.g., "discoverer" with role "qa", "impl" with role "developer").

To find an agent's window for sending messages:
```bash
grep -A 4 "name: discoverer" .workflow/*/agents.yml | grep "window:" | awk '{print $2}'
```

Always check agents.yml for the correct agent name and window number before sending messages.
The agents.yml file is the source of truth for all agent locations and sessions.
